OL,4,C'skinny jab' ads targeting 'vulnerable
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FThe UK's advertising watchdog has told
OL,8,FITV News it will tackle "illegal,
OL,9,Funacceptable and unfair" adverts for
OL,10,Fweight-loss injections, which are
OL,11,Fputting "extremely vulnerable" people
OL,12,Fat risk.
OL,14,FIt comes as the National Institute for
OL,15,FHealth and Care Excellence (NICE) has
OL,16,Fannounced details for the roll-out of
OL,17,Fa new weight-loss injection on the NHS
OL,18,F` though fewer than 10% of patients in
OL,19,FEngland who are eligible will
OL,20,Finitially be able to access it.
