OL,7,FA recent investigation by ITV News
OL,8,Fexposed the potentially fatal side
OL,9,Feffects of obesity drugs, especially
OL,10,Fif used without the proper regulation
OL,11,Fand medical guidance.
OL,13,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,14,F(ASA) says it is concerned by the
OL,15,F"huge proliferation" of weight-loss
OL,16,Fpromotions online and, having detected
OL,17,Fthousands of potentially rule-breaking
OL,18,Fadverts in recent months, is warning
OL,19,Fadvertisers to "stick to the rules or
OL,20,Fface sanctions".
