OL,7,FWeight-loss drugs like Wegovy
OL,8,F(semaglutide), Saxenda (liraglutide)
OL,9,Fand Mounjaro (tirzepatide) are
OL,10,Fprescription-only medications.
OL,12,FUK laws and advertising rules prohibit
OL,13,Fthem from being advertised to the
OL,14,Fpublic.
OL,16,FBut they are regularly being promoted
OL,17,Fon social media and in online adverts,
OL,18,Fwith the medications sometimes
OL,19,Fdescribed as 'skinny jabs'.
