OL,7,F"I was unhappy, I wanted a quick fix"
OL,8,FLauren Redford-Hughes from Darlington
OL,9,Ftold ITV News.
OL,11,FThe mother-of-three saw an advert on
OL,12,Fsocial media and paid #120 for one
OL,13,Fmonth's supply of injections, but soon
OL,14,Fbecame unwell.
OL,16,F"I woke up and I had excruciating
OL,17,Fstomach pain. I was lying in bed
OL,18,Fthinking this could be it for me - but
OL,19,Fmy kids need me. I felt like an idiot."
