OL,7,FShe thinks more must be done to tackle
OL,8,Fthe adverts.
OL,10,F"They're just everywhere, you look on
OL,11,FTikTok and there are girls bragging
OL,12,Fthat they can't eat anything. Things
OL,13,Fneed to be regulated."
OL,15,FThe ASA told ITV News it is now
OL,16,Framping up its investigations into
OL,17,F"irresponsible" advertisers.
