OL,7,F"We are concerned about the sheer
OL,8,Fscale and number of these
OL,9,Fadvertisements," Baroness Nicky
OL,10,FMorgan, chair of the Advertising
OL,11,FStandards Authority, told ITV News.
OL,13,FArtificial intelligence tools are
OL,14,Fbeing employed by the ASA, allowing
OL,15,Fthem to monitor 3.5 million social
OL,16,Fmedia posts and digital adverts every
OL,17,Fmonth.
