OL,7,FSince August they've discovered more
OL,8,Fthan 2,000 adverts for weight-loss
OL,9,Fdrugs, suspected of breaching the
OL,10,Frules.
OL,12,FBaroness Nicky Morgan, a former
OL,13,FConservative Minister, was appointed
OL,14,Fas chair of the ASA last month.
OL,16,F"We are seeing a huge proliferation of
OL,17,Fthese advertisements aimed at the
OL,18,Fpublic, which are illegal,
OL,19,Funacceptable and unfair to people who
OL,20,Fare often extremely vulnerable - and
OL,21,Fthey need to stop," she said.
