OL,7,FITV News previously revealed that the
OL,8,FUK's drugs regulator, the MHRA, has
OL,9,Fbeen alerted to 18 deaths with
OL,10,Fsuspected links to weight-loss
OL,11,Finjections since 2020.
OL,13,F"You have highlighted cases where
OL,14,Fpeople have not been prescribed these
OL,15,Fmedicines by a medical professional -
OL,16,Fand have come to harm," said Baroness
OL,17,FMorgan.
