OL,7,F"That's why our message to companies,
OL,8,Finfluencers and businesses is they
OL,9,Fmust not be advertising these
OL,10,Fprescription only medicines."
OL,12,FThe ASA has removed a number of
OL,13,Fadverts promoting weight-loss
OL,14,Finjections, but so far no advertiser
OL,15,Fhas been fined or prosecuted.
OL,17,FBaroness Morgan told ITV News she
OL,18,Fbelieves internet companies have the
OL,19,F"capability" to prevent potentially
OL,20,Fharmful adverts appearing online.
