OL,7,FBut to "protect" NHS services from
OL,8,Fbeing overwhelmed by demand, Mounjaro
OL,9,F(tirzepatide) will initially only be
OL,10,Fgiven to people with the "highest
OL,11,Fclinical need" - those with a body
OL,12,Fmass index of more than 35 and at
OL,13,Fleast one weight-related illness.
OL,15,FNICE says around a quarter of a
OL,16,Fmillion people will receive the drug
OL,17,Fon the NHS over the next three years.
OL,19,FThat's fewer than 10% of people in
OL,20,FEngland who are eligible.
